MudraVaani – Bridging Communication Through Indian Sign Language
Overview

MudraVaani is an AI-assisted web application designed to improve communication accessibility for the Deaf and Hard-of-Hearing community. The platform converts English text into Indian Sign Language (ISL) gloss and plays corresponding sign videos, while also providing learning resources, live communication, and community-driven video uploads.

Features

✅ English to Indian Sign Language conversion

✅ NLP-based sentence simplification using spaCy & Stanza

✅ ISL Gloss generation

✅ Video-based sign playback

✅ Learn Sign interactive module

✅ Community video upload portal

✅ Live video calling with signaling

✅ Feedback system

